232
 Erman Erbaykal
isbn belirtilmemiş
1. Baskı
Graphic Design in Television Decor
https://imageserver.kitapyurdu.com/select.php?imageid=3057114&width=500&isWatermarked=true
2017-01-27
 74,38
Television, influencing the last century aside, presents the audience many fictional worlds. Television shows created in studios are used for this dream marketing stuff. After the main topic of the show, decor and the decoration of the decor is what makes a program watchable. The objective of the use of color, lighting furnishing and electronic components is to increase the audience. With the race for the viewers between the modern day television broadcasters details are vital. The most important of these details is the graphic elements in decor.Being only a separator at the beginning, graphic design in television decor is now an important and irreplaceable section of broadcasting. My research in this regard studies the graphic elements used in Turkish discussion programs.The aim of this study is to find the criterions that dominate the layout of decor and the graphic elements in decor and to research the graphic design of the discussion programs on Turkish national television.The subjects and related chapters are; in the first chapter decoration and the elements of decoration, television decoration and its types. In the second chapter; graphic elements in decoration. In this chapter photography illustration moving graphics color and typography are included. In the third chapter, discussion program types and its decorations program type and graphic element relation is researched. 
112
 İpek Fatma Çevik
